element BankAccountBaseDetailsGroup/Address
diagram
type W4C_Address
properties
minOcc 0
maxOcc unbounded
content complex
annotation
appinfo
Bank address information. It can be present as in local language as in English.
                            Following fields are supported in local language (Language != "ENG"): Country, AddressZip,
                            City, AddressLocation, AddressLine1, AddressLine2, AddressLine3, AddressLine4, and
                            MunicipalityCode. Following fields are supported in English (Language = "ENG"): City,
                            AddressLine1, AddressLine2, AddressLine3, and AddressLine4

complexType W4DC_Extra
diagram

element W4DC_Extra/Type
diagram
type W4D_Code
properties
content simple
facets
Kind Value Annotation
minLength 1
maxLength 32
annotation
appinfo
Type of Extra information. Supported values:
                        AddInfo - additional informaion;
                        CustomAddInfo - Custom data in tag-value format;
                        CustomData - Custom Data in Bertlv format;
                        SrcFee - Source Fee;
                        TgtFee - Target Fee;
                        Fee - Fee;
                        CustomFee - Custom Fee;
                        Surcharge - Fee charged by merchant for the operation
                        SrcTrn - Source Amount;
                        TgtTrn - Target Amount;
                        Auth - Authorization (blocked) Amount;
                        PaymentProperties - additional properties of a payment;
                        OriginalData - original interchange file data;
                        SrcAddFee - Additional Source Contract Fee linked to service and filtered by pipe parameter
                        CUSTOM_FEE_CODES;
                        ExtOperationDtls - Extended details of operation;
                        AncillaryServiceCharge - Additional MC service charges;
                        TgtAddFee - Additional Target Contract Fee linked to service and filtered by pipe parameter
                        CUSTOM_FEE_CODES.
                        Purchase - information from TPURCHASE_AMOUNT and TPURCHASE_CURR tags from addInfo;
                        Cashback - information from TCASHBACK_AMOUNT and TCASHBACK_CURR tags from addInfo;
